				>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/tikoam.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Tikoam</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Remplacement total d'inDesign pour l'agence Tikoam
							par un outil sur-mesure pour composer des mémoires
							techniques et portfolios à plusieurs, à la vitesse
							de l'éclair.
						</p>
						<small class="leading-0">Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://laurasavignac.com">Laura Savignac</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/sequences.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Séquences</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Base de données métier complète on-prem, édition
							multisupports avancée, multi-utilisateur, API
							publique, sites web autogénérés, extensibilité.<br
							/>La première instance d'Alzo !
						</p>
						<small class="leading-0">Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://laurasavignac.com">Laura Savignac</a> et <a class="underlined" href="https://a-regular.com/">atelier regular</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/amm.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Architecture Malacan Martres</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Automatisation des supports de présentation concours
							et site web via un backoffice unifié.
						</p>
						<small class="leading-0">Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/johanna-larosa/">Johanna Larosa Développement & Communication</a><br/>et <a class="underlined" href="https://laurasavignac.com">Laura Savignac</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/duffau.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Duffau &Associés</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Automatisation des supports de présentation concours
							et site web via un backoffice unifié, génération
							d'images, pipeline d'édition de books remplaçant
							inDesign.
						</p>
						<small class="leading-0">Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://laurasavignac.com">Laura Savignac</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/lcr.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">LCR Architectes</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Automatisation des supports de présentation et site
							web via un backoffice unifié.
						</p>
						<small class="leading-0">Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/johanna-larosa/">Johanna Larosa Développement & Communication</a><br/>et <a class="underlined" href="https://laurasavignac.com">Laura Savignac</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/scalene.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Scalène</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Base de données métier complète, édition
							multisupports avancée, API publique, sites web
							autogénérés. Un projet précurseur d'alzo !
						</p>
						<small>Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://documents.design/">atelier documents</a></small>
					</div>
					<div
						class="p-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
						style="flex: 0 0 300px"
					>
						<div
							class="w-32 h-32 mb-4 rounded-full bg-white flex justify-center items-center"
						>
							<img
								src="/logos/execo.png"
								class="w-16 h-16 object-contain opacity-75"
								style="filter: grayscale(1); background-blend-mode: screen;"
							/>
						</div>
						<h3 class="fs-t4 mb-4">Execo</h3>
						<p class="fs-t5 text-center text-[#0085C8]/70">
							Automatisation de supports de présentations.
						</p>
						<small>Avec <a class="underlined" href="https://a-regular.com/">atelier regular</a></small>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section
			class="bg-isabelline text-brand text-center p-4 md:p-10 relative"
		>
			<h2 class="md:text-6xl text-4xl mb-8">Fonctionnalités</h2>

			<div class="hidden md:flex justify-center gap-8 sticky top-14 bg-isabelline p-4 z-20 w-full rounded-full shadow-sm">
				<a href="#memoire-agence" data-fades-by-scroll="" class="border border-brand transition bg-brand text-white rounded-full p-2">Mémoire d'agence</a>
				<a href="#gen-documents" data-fades-by-scroll="" class="border border-brand transition rounded-full p-2">Génération de documents</a>
				<a href="#collaboration" data-fades-by-scroll="" class="border border-brand transition rounded-full p-2">Collaboration</a>
				<a href="#integration-technique" data-fades-by-scroll="" class="border border-brand transition rounded-full p-2">Intégrations et technique</a>
			</div>

			<div class="mb-12 md:mb-40">
				<h3 class="md:text-4xl text-xl mb-4 mt-8" id="memoire-agence">Mémoire d'agence</h3>
				<div class="relative inline-block md:min-w-[540px]">
					<table
						class="text-xs md:text-base text-left relative z-10 rounded-md md:max-w-[540px] mx-auto"
					>
						<tbody>
							<tr>
								<td class="border-brand border-y py-2 px-4"
